Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.52,0:00:03.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnArial Black\pos(316,325)\fad(400,0)}Obey the Rules and manners\Nto have a fun Duel!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.52,0:00:19.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Light so glaring that it can't be hidden shatters the silence and revives in this world
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.50,0:00:30.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The violently quaking and thirsty Earth stakes its life and clashes together with sparks
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.28,0:00:38.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just one more time is enough to create a miracle
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.45,0:00:45.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}For the power to regain the pages of memory lost in the past
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.40,0:00:53.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fs30}The believing heart that penetrates the darkness searches for the place where its soul sleeps
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.69,0:00:59.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And burns a sharp glance of eyes that can't sparkle
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.10,0:01:07.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Two hearts of light and shadow head toward the future that the crystal reflects
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.42,0:01:13.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now they start to move, these eyes brimming red
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.10,0:01:29.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In Bakura's battle against the priests,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.13,0:01:31.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Bakura held an overwhelming advantage,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.47,0:01:34.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}aiding Diabound with power from the dead spirits.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.14,0:01:38.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just as Kalim fell and we thought we had no chance of victory,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.18,0:01:41.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}the soul of my father, Akhenamkhanen,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.25,0:01:44.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}manifested and lead the spirits into the World of the Dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.35,0:01:45.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now, Mahado!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.52,0:01:47.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Finish Diabound off!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.79,0:01:51.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This match is over, Bakura!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.09,0:01:57.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"A New Stage"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.54,0:02:07.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all that, we still can't enter...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.51,0:02:13.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If there are any clues about the other me's name, they have to be within this palace!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.75,0:02:16.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Other Me...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.05,0:02:21.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If you want to win this game, you have to obtain your lost name!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.09,0:02:22.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We finally understand that now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.72,0:02:28.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We came to this world so we could find your true name that's been lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.69,0:02:30.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So please...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.26,0:02:35.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Let us enter the palace, Other... Me...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.80,0:02:39.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can enter!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.14,0:02:40.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay! We can enter!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.44,0:02:43.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.71,0:02:48.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's gotta be a toooon of food to eat in there~!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.45,0:02:51.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bobasa's gonna eat 'till he bursts!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.25,0:02:54.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go look for the other me's name!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.72,0:02:55.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Let's!\N - Let's!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.59,0:02:57.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold up, Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.69,0:02:58.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.26,0:02:59.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bobasa's coming too~!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.73,0:03:10.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Awesome~!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.07,0:03:11.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is the palace!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.60,0:03:15.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's so large. There's no telling where it could be around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.67,0:03:18.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's all split up and search!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.51,0:03:19.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.48,0:03:27.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi... Damn you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.05,0:03:29.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just you wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.39,0:03:31.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll rip all of your lives right out of you...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.56,0:03:36.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll steal all the Millennium Items and obtain the Power of Darkness for myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.74,0:03:47.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it...!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.87,0:03:50.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no use, Bakura!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.01,0:03:54.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as we're holding the remaining Millennium Items,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.05,0:03:57.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you won't be able to break the seal on Zorc!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.38,0:03:59.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.89,0:04:07.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just give up, Bakura. You've lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.86,0:04:10.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.13,0:04:12.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lord Akhenaden!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.03,0:04:20.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now everything required for the revival ritual has been gathered together!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.41,0:04:21.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.48,0:04:26.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.94,0:04:28.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Shada's Millennium Ankh!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.91,0:04:31.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is the meaning of this, Lord Akehnaden?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.48,0:04:35.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The time has finally come!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.20,0:04:48.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Where am I...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.67,0:04:51.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just what... am I doing...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.60,0:04:54.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What the...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.91,0:04:56.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.97,0:04:58.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Good work.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.68,0:05:00.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I no longer have any use for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.45,0:05:02.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That voice...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.65,0:05:05.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.05,0:05:06.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Help me...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.15,0:05:07.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help m-
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.29,0:05:15.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The {\i0}rules{\i1} state that when a {\i0}pawn{\i1}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.29,0:05:17.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}is no longer needed, it disappears, Yugi...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.90,0:05:19.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pawn?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.37,0:05:22.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lord... Akhenaden...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.44,0:05:26.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shada!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.38,0:05:31.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.61,0:05:34.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Pharaoh's name...\N The Pharaoh's name...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.48,0:05:35.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no use.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.85,0:05:39.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if the other me's name is written here,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.48,0:05:40.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't read it at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.86,0:05:46.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Er...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.32,0:05:49.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I gotta question for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.13,0:05:50.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,About the Pharaoh's-
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.46,0:05:54.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Oh yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.47,0:05:57.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're about the equivalent of {\i1}ghosts{\i0} here...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.81,0:06:05.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's got to be around this place somewhere...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.04,0:06:09.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I can't touch any of the books...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.11,0:06:10.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.58,0:06:12.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How am I supposed to search like this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.85,0:06:18.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bobasa likes eating more than he likes searching!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.79,0:06:20.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lemme dig in!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.66,0:06:21.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The "Bo" in...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.23,0:06:26.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.20,0:06:29.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Eighth Key... The Pharaoh's name!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.20,0:06:30.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shada!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.44,0:06:34.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lord Akhenaden...! That's my Millennium Ankh...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.44,0:06:37.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please return it, Lord Akehnaden!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.71,0:06:39.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.75,0:06:41.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shada!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.31,0:06:43.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You half-dead worm!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.45,0:06:46.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir Akehnaden! Why are you doing this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.35,0:06:47.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you gone {\i1}mad?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.85,0:06:50.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the meaning of this, Akehnaden?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.52,0:06:51.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell us your reason!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.82,0:06:54.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmph. How arrogant you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.33,0:06:58.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lord Akhenaden! Talking to the Pharaoh with such dirty words...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.46,0:07:01.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it is you, Lord Akehnaden, I will not allow for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.33,0:07:02.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut your mouth!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.20,0:07:05.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Seto?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.38,0:07:12.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe I said "the time has come"...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.61,0:07:17.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My body...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.05,0:07:21.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How does it feel being unable to move, Pharaoh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.12,0:07:23.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What have you done, Akehnaden?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.99,0:07:31.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the power of the almighty Zorc, controller of time...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.10,0:07:32.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...time has been stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.90,0:07:36.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At this moment, the only one permitted to move...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.43,0:07:38.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...is myself, and myself alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.94,0:07:43.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmph. You are an heir hardly qualified to be Pharaoh!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.41,0:07:46.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Millennium Rod!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.88,0:07:49.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Millennium Tauk!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.05,0:07:51.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.12,0:07:54.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the final piece lies {\i1}right here!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.89,0:07:57.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sir Akhenaden!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.39,0:07:58.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Lord Akhenaden!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.12,0:08:00.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Stop this!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.06,0:08:05.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All of the Millennium Items have now been gathered!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.03,0:08:10.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Akhenaden! Place all the Millennium Items within the stone tablet!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.87,0:08:12.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.27,0:08:15.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why has the Dark Game not ended when Bakura is dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.87,0:08:18.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And why am I still hearing Bakura's voice,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.48,0:08:21.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}despite him turning to sand and disappearing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.62,0:08:30.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Become or key to victory...\N Resurrect the Great Evil God, Zorc!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.46,0:08:36.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.43,0:08:39.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why have I not won, even after defeating Bakura?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.53,0:08:41.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why has time stopped?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.20,0:08:45.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just how long is this Dark Game going to continue?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.30,0:08:47.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Game...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.21,0:08:49.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the last one.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.34,0:08:54.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's it! This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.02,0:09:06.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see you've finally awoken as the Game Master...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.22,0:09:07.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Yugi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.36,0:09:09.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bakura?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.49,0:09:10.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this place?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.43,0:09:11.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"This place"...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.53,0:09:12.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.63,0:09:15.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess you could call this\N "Domain of the Gods".
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.47,0:09:19.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This before you is the true form of the Ultimate Dark Game.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.20,0:09:20.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Dark R.P.G.!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.97,0:09:23.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dark R.P.G.?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.41,0:09:24.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.34,0:09:27.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The setting of the game is Ancient Egypt.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.18,0:09:31.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi, this field is a reproduction of the world you lived in 3,000 years ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.58,0:09:34.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where you ruled as Pharaoh.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.52,0:09:37.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As the Game Masters, we control the characters.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.29,0:09:40.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you clear the conditions required for victory, you win.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.49,0:09:43.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then that makes my character the Pharaoh.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.49,0:09:46.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you are Thief King Bakura.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.56,0:09:49.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But now that Bakura has been defeated,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.17,0:09:51.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I should have cleared my required conditions for victory!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.87,0:09:53.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So then, why?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.67,0:09:56.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Too {\i1}bad,{\i0} Yugi...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.14,0:09:58.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that the seven Millennium Items
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.91,0:10:01.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,have been placed in the Stone Tablet of the Underworld,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.41,0:10:03.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the game has welcomed a new stage!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.98,0:10:06.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naturally, the conditions for victory have {\i1}changed!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.45,0:10:10.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My soul rests with the Stone Tablet of the Underworld!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.25,0:10:13.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And shall be resurrected along with the Great Wicked God, Zorc!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.73,0:10:19.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So in short, if I don't defeat Zorc,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.53,0:10:21.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to lose?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.67,0:10:23.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You won't just {\i1}lose!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.53,0:10:24.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.27,0:10:26.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All of your little {\i1}precious partners{\i0} who
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.07,0:10:28.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,transcended the labyrinth within the Millennium Puzzle
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.24,0:10:33.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and snuck into the game without permission in order to find you...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.24,0:10:34.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...will die right where they stand.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.51,0:10:38.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They will {\i1}die.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.35,0:10:43.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Curse you, Bakura!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.74,0:11:01.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to save your little precious partners,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.41,0:11:03.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,your only option is to {\i1}beat{\i0} me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.44,0:11:06.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But currently, none of your characters can move.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.85,0:11:09.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because of {\i1}this thing's{\i0} effect.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.58,0:11:10.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.82,0:11:12.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My Master Item.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.62,0:11:13.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Time Controlling Hourglass.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.92,0:11:15.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Master Item, you said?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.92,0:11:17.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.39,0:11:20.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,While this item sits out on the field,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.56,0:11:24.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,all characters I don't recognize are robbed of their movement!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.00,0:11:26.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Time Controlling Hourglass?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.30,0:11:32.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And my {\i1}other item{\i0} is {\i1}this!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.10,0:11:34.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you {\i1}remember,{\i0} Yugi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.34,0:11:39.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I used this to turn time backwards and force your little friends away from you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.16,0:11:58.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was {\i1}you?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.90,0:12:04.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. That was the result of my Time Reversing Hourglass.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.94,0:12:06.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And Yugi...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.40,0:12:08.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have something else to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.67,0:12:12.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can activate its special effects up to three times.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.44,0:12:14.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meaning I can once again...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.41,0:12:17.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...use my Master Item another time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.29,0:12:24.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What's going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.89,0:12:28.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why won't my body move?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.09,0:12:31.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Does this mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.00,0:12:35.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...something big is \Ngoing on with my other self?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.17,0:12:38.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Shit...! What the hell's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.74,0:12:41.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What's the deal?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.37,0:12:46.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Right now, the only ones allowed to move are those I acknowledge.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.44,0:12:47.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}How is he able to move!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.68,0:12:54.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how much I eat, my stomach won't fill up at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.72,0:12:56.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Almighty Wicked God Zorc!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.99,0:12:59.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please hear the wish I beseech of thee!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.06,0:13:03.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He's contacting something enormous, something terrifying...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.70,0:13:05.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I feel a wave of wickedness!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.23,0:13:07.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You must not resurrect it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.57,0:13:10.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}High Priest Akhenaden...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.13,0:13:15.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I knew you would come here to complete the Dark Contract with me...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.87,0:13:22.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Because {\i0}you{\i1} are the one who brought the Millennium Items into this world!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.58,0:13:26.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Akhenaden... Rule the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.32,0:13:32.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Become the slave of my soul... and I shall grant your wish!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.09,0:13:34.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yes! I have but one wish!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.99,0:13:38.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I wish to make my son, Seto,\N into the king!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.83,0:13:40.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What did he...!?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.20,0:13:41.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Seto is...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.93,0:13:44.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm... I am...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.57,0:13:48.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Lord Akhenaden's... son?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.01,0:13:51.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have heard your wish!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.28,0:13:55.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Take my power within you, Akhenaden!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.52,0:14:02.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Akhenaden!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.13,0:14:11.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At this moment,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.00,0:14:13.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Akhenaden has gained the skills of a Dark Magician
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.43,0:14:14.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and he levels up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.20,0:14:17.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's become the High Priest of Darkness!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.07,0:14:18.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.00,0:14:20.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The High Priest of Darkness?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.00,0:14:23.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi, you may not remember it,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.84,0:14:27.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but history is repeating itself exactly as it did before!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.61,0:14:30.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although, some {\i1}minor details{\i0} have changed slightly...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.01,0:14:32.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that doesn't change the fact that the history
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.22,0:14:35.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,of what happened 3,000 years ago is repeating itself once again!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.02,0:14:42.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Back then, you gave your own life in order to seal Zorc away.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.53,0:14:45.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that won't be happening {\i1}this time{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.46,0:14:48.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Great Wicked God Zorc {\i1}will{\i0} revive...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.00,0:14:49.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And he shall turn this world into a {\i1}paradise{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.73,0:14:51.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,of destruction and ruin!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.47,0:14:52.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Behold!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.84,0:14:55.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At my third Master Item!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.51,0:14:57.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.54,0:14:59.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that the seven Millennium Items have
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.68,0:15:02.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,been placed into the Stone Tablet of the Underworld,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.28,0:15:05.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the third hourglass, the Hourglass of Isolated Desperation,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.48,0:15:07.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,can now be activated!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.15,0:15:07.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.55,0:15:09.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the Hourglass of Isolated Desperation?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.79,0:15:13.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The last spec of sand that falls from this hourglass...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.23,0:15:17.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...will usher in the moment \Nof Zorc's revival!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.74,0:15:28.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I found the hidden room which holds the secrets of
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.91,0:15:31.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}all generations of the Pharaohs.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.54,0:15:34.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The previous Pharaoh, Akhenamkhanen.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.95,0:15:38.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The name of the current Pharaoh should be listed after his.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.55,0:15:40.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.69,0:15:43.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What is going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.12,0:15:46.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His name's {\i1}not written{\i0} here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.89,0:15:49.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now, my Priest of Darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.53,0:15:54.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If you eliminate the Pharaoh right now, your wish shall be granted!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.87,0:15:59.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}H-He said my father...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.07,0:16:03.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Lord Akhenaden... is my... Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.18,0:16:07.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My father never came home after that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.71,0:16:10.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And you're telling me Lord Akhenaden
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.82,0:16:12.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}turns out to be that very same dad?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.78,0:16:16.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me tell you, my son, Seto.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.25,0:16:19.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The truth that the former king, Akhenamkhanen, is my brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.79,0:16:20.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.96,0:16:25.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Akhenaden is the little brother of my father, Akhenamkhanen?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.17,0:16:28.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.87,0:16:32.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...is the truth that only myself and Sir Akhenaden knows of currently!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.57,0:16:37.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's a secret the two of us swore to keep to ourselves!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.74,0:16:40.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And why {\i0}now,{\i1} of all times...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.05,0:16:43.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why are you breaking that promise?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.01,0:16:45.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because you, my son, Seto,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.68,0:16:49.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,are the most fitting to rule as a rightful king!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.52,0:16:52.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meaning that if you rid yourself of all the obstacles,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.42,0:16:56.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you can steal the throne and reign over this country!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.50,0:17:02.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Weep as, right here and now,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.27,0:17:06.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seto becomes the new king of this country!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.08,0:17:23.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The attack was repelled before it could make contact!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.35,0:17:26.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! He's protecting the Pharaoh!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.42,0:17:27.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who {\i1}is{\i0} this guy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.16,0:17:29.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bakura...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.86,0:17:32.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You{\i0} aren't the {\i1}only one{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.63,0:17:34.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,holding a Master Item, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.90,0:17:36.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.10,0:17:39.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who {\i1}are{\i0} you, fiend?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.50,0:17:43.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You,{\i0} who dares to repel my attack and protect the Pharaoh!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.88,0:17:45.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Hasan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.88,0:17:48.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The former Pharaoh has given me the duty to protect this land of Egypt
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.91,0:17:50.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,, and the great Pharaoh.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.02,0:17:55.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As the late Akhenamkhanen wished, I shall protect you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.89,0:17:57.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hasan...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.89,0:17:59.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's you from before...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.23,0:18:03.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Who {\i0}are{\i1} you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.83,0:18:05.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My name is Hasan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.26,0:18:06.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hasan?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.43,0:18:11.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Pharaoh, the Great Wicked God Zorc is about to revive.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.00,0:18:13.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Only {\i0}you{\i1} can defeat Zorc!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.14,0:18:15.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hasan, or whoever you are...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.54,0:18:18.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If an insect like you truly has the ability to communicate
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.04,0:18:20.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,with my brother, the late Akhenamkhanen...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.95,0:18:22.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell my brother {\i1}this!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.45,0:18:25.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That the only one deserving of having the glory to rule as king
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.28,0:18:28.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is my son, Seto!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.12,0:18:29.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I shall not listen to the ramblings of someone
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.95,0:18:33.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who heeds to the soul of the Great Wicked God Zorc to satisfy
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.26,0:18:35.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,his own desires!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.73,0:18:40.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.10,0:18:48.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Time Controlling Hourglass...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.87,0:18:52.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I am free to move as I please!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.64,0:18:54.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My {\i1}friends,{\i0} I mean!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.95,0:18:58.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M-My body...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.15,0:19:00.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you able to move?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.02,0:19:03.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Only those I permit are supposed to be able to move!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.99,0:19:05.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,High Priest of Darkness...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.19,0:19:09.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Time has begun to move once again!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.29,0:19:13.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Curse you... Hasan!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.13,0:19:15.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure did screw me over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.57,0:19:18.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's a little {\i1}too early{\i0}\N to rest at ease, Yugi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.90,0:19:22.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take a look at the gauges of your pieces!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.31,0:19:24.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? What do you mean, gauges?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.24,0:19:28.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the gauge of their {\i1}souls{\i0} which lies on the DiaDhanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.68,0:19:31.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My{\i0} piece, High Priest of Darkness,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.18,0:19:33.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is operating at full power level right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.28,0:19:34.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Your{\i0} pieces, however...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.39,0:19:44.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyone whose gauge reaches zero {\i1}crosses over{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.10,0:19:48.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And if the Pharaoh is injured in battle, his {\i1}Ba{\i0} gauge depleted...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.33,0:19:50.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...you {\i1}yourself{\i0} will die alongside him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.17,0:19:52.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And not only {\i1}you{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.24,0:19:53.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your {\i1}friends{\i0} as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.01,0:19:56.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.67,0:19:58.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This includes all the people in this world!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.74,0:20:00.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They {\i1}all{\i0} have a {\i1}Ba{\i0} gauge!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.98,0:20:04.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But since most of them don't have a DiaDhank...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.45,0:20:07.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...it's impossible to know how much {\i1}Ba{\i0} they have remaining...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.52,0:20:09.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and they blindly wander the city,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.12,0:20:12.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,believing tomorrow will\N come as it always does.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.56,0:20:15.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Goodness, what {\i1}ignorant{\i0} people they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.23,0:20:17.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They don't even know that the two of us are
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.06,0:20:18.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,deciding whether they {\i1}live or die!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.76,0:20:20.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, Yugi...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.63,0:20:22.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How many civilians do you suppose
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.63,0:20:26.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,have been killed during our previous battles?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.30,0:20:28.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bakura! You {\i1}monster!!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.84,0:20:30.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, there!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.64,0:20:32.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't try to act like you're innocent!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.71,0:20:35.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And don't try to tell me you aren't just as responsible.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.71,0:20:39.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since you were, you know, {\i1}in{\i0} the battles as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.02,0:20:42.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen well! This is a battle of {\i1}Gods!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.32,0:20:43.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As far is this game is concerned,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.45,0:20:45.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the two of us are {\i1}divine Gods!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.12,0:20:47.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And he who dominates this R.P.G....
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.99,0:20:50.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...will become the God of all Gods!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.37,0:20:57.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bakura, don't lump me together with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.20,0:21:00.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no intentions of becoming a god!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.37,0:21:03.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just want to protect my friends and this world...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.74,0:21:06.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...from everything, \Nno matter what happens!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.74,0:21:08.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Prattle as much as you like, Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.91,0:21:11.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I plan to become the Wicked God of this world...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.42,0:21:14.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and become the key that unlocks destruction and terror!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.45,0:21:16.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I plan to {\i1}show you{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.75,0:21:19.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the {\i1}end of this world{\i0} as we know it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.13,0:21:24.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You {\i1}scum!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.96,0:21:26.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Too little, too late!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.07,0:21:31.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because the {\i1}countdown to Armageddon{\i0} has begun!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.76,0:21:59.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}To show us now...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.03,0:22:08.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...a map isn't needed.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.54,0:22:14.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Only what tore apart the darkness...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.68,0:22:24.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...the hope that lies in my hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.79,0:22:29.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Without deciding on a goal...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.19,0:22:38.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll just take a step toward my dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.84,0:22:44.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}EYE'S, while I feel them...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.34,0:22:52.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll find your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.95,0:22:58.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh! EYE'S, if what I wished for...
